    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This RFC suggests a simple method for workstations to dynamically access mail from a mailbox server.  This RFC specifies a proposed protocol for the ARPA-Internet community, and requests discussion and suggestions for improvement.  This memo is a revision of RFC-918.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
